rows.label: qst200420_0010
rows.name: Why... won't you finish me off?

rows.label: qst200420_0020
rows.name:
...I do not kill. Not even
a villain such as you.

rows.label: qst200420_0030
rows.name: ...Heh. What's this about not killing?

rows.label: qst200420_0040
rows.name: Don't give me that sweet talk.

rows.label: qst200420_0050
rows.name:
Even if you don't do it,
someone else will kill them.

rows.label: qst200420_0060
rows.name: ...Just like that woman. Everyone dies.

rows.label: qst200420_0070
rows.name: Vasara.

rows.label: qst200420_0080
rows.name:
Your skills... They are
skills for killing people.

rows.label: qst200420_0090
rows.name: You haven't changed at all.

rows.label: qst200420_0100
rows.name:
No matter how many times you're reborn,
it's the same. You're just a killer.

rows.label: qst200420_0110
rows.name:
As proof, right now, you're
dying to kill me, aren't you?

rows.label: qst200420_0120
rows.name: What's wrong? Kill me.

rows.label: qst200420_0130
rows.name:
You hate me, don't you? You can't
let a villain live, can you?

rows.label: qst200420_0140
rows.name: Then don't hold back. Kill me, Vasara.

rows.label: qst200420_0150
rows.name: And reclaim your old self.

rows.label: qst200420_0160
rows.name: ...I will not kill.

rows.label: qst200420_0170
rows.name:
I will not grant you an
end as easy as death.

rows.label: qst200420_0180
rows.name:
From now on, you will spend your
entire life atoning for your sins.

rows.label: qst200420_0190
rows.name: That's... worse than death, isn't it...

rows.label: qst200420_0200
rows.name: You really are... the Heartless Judge...
